# create-agent-skill-repo

Create a personal agent-skills repository for Claude Code.

```bash
uvx create-agent-skill-repo
```

With GitHub integration:

```bash
uvx create-agent-skill-repo --github
```

See [agent-skills](https://upd.dev/skills/agent-skills-project) for full documentation.
